{"tid":400744,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「發夢」如果國際表決支國馬上全面吞併北泡","createTime":"2017-09-15T05:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T17:45:37.000Z","uid":14055,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22fde5b1ac6d41124ae419e3c66eade48f4fb821","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"眼見現時金仔痴q咗線係咁對世界挑釁，老美都冇晒辦法，個個都只能依靠支國制衡北泡，如果有一日全球接納支國全面接管北泡，協助一齊打倒金仔，大家認為會有什麼影響？"},{"pid":"8984c18e07aea0d837c53cacfe318cc3c1654d4f","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"申利：「只係發夢，唔洗認真」"},{"pid":"f20535b74ac02c11cd4d6e5d329aeb6f69a1d93f","tid":400744,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"南泡一定反對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白頭山(長白山)是我們的.jpg"},{"pid":"13e772488192aa23eaf55680b407dad55808a79b","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南泡一定反對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白頭山(長白山)是我們的.jpg</blockquote><br />\n南泡依家驚到瀨屎，反條毛咩"},{"pid":"ae30722b54bf1620374166e61faada327fcc784d","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:46:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2a6797d38237146ff43ff21e1ed6aa7fc61d283","tid":400744,"uid":35585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"金仔會統一全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7983003c7504b2f068b30cf752593b24ad79a5","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔會統一全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辣殺"},{"pid":"20336addb1d9c42dd9632fab5770fcae05e96d9f","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"連登仔淨識盲屌，講深入少少已經技窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779548e1badda817c140a0419f84766798ca8c3f","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2b4f60bb9432ebd559e49c9d58471f588399ef","tid":400744,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:59:21.000Z","msg":"唔覺得支國有咁傻"},{"pid":"b4d89f5b72e4ad76e010c67c8e7433c33a38e37c","tid":400744,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"支那依家發緊圍,一打又要窮幾十幾百年"},{"pid":"cb8b7d2b17db7458f17b74e2fbc3afc1201c5153","tid":400744,"uid":142725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"吞完接收幾百萬飢民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cf68d79a6ce7a67db4020ea436f9a49ddf8bb6","tid":400744,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"北京爆蘑菇雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aa373dc1e36a570814f69a21a46bae7d486747","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺得支國有咁傻</blockquote><br />\n痴線，一啲都唔傻"},{"pid":"331f36912aafc93808b12359ed641a8bc9120b88","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吞完接收幾百萬飢民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個數點得出黎架？"},{"pid":"5afc55be6524a0e7185c729a612347c98e9559e6","tid":400744,"uid":1080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:53:37.000Z","msg":"如果支共真係要咁做 打完好大機會之後扶植一個政權 維持南北泡現狀"},{"pid":"312f38db0bf73affed930f39c0eff98c64e7002f","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那依家發緊圍,一打又要窮幾十幾百年</blockquote><br />\n痴線，架仔同南泡都怕支國嘅軍事實力，區區金仔小意思，要打好快KO，只係大家都簽咗條約唔打核戰，就得金仔呢條頑童唔聽話，如果佢再搞搞震，一家會叫支國幫手食q咗佢，不過支國都唔蠢，放任個頑童搞到大家陣腳大亂，佢自己做下花生友都唔知幾happy"},{"pid":"48bbe44b6a84b4358cf3c6ccce248a1d108899f8","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果支共真係要咁做 打完好大機會之後扶植一個政權 維持南北泡現狀</blockquote><br />\n只要唔係金仔話事，大家就會冇咁驚"},{"pid":"e43b1dce9362edc19b1d14d5612bd553ba40fa62","tid":400744,"uid":1080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果支共真係要咁做 打完好大機會之後扶植一個政權 維持南北泡現狀</blockquote><br />\n只要唔係金仔話事，大家就會冇咁驚</blockquote><br />\n當然要發生呢個情況既前題係 金仔真係完全不受控制 否則中國好大機會都係比佢玩落去"},{"pid":"681e59dc782911232a9da9d42624b0f7ca9f5e3c","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果支共真係要咁做 打完好大機會之後扶植一個政權 維持南北泡現狀</blockquote><br />\n只要唔係金仔話事，大家就會冇咁驚</blockquote><br />\n當然要發生呢個情況既前題係 金仔真係完全不受控制 否則中國好大機會都係比佢玩落去</blockquote><br />\n大家都睇緊侵侵頭"},{"pid":"72572915acdbba24280a5ffd5a2fe2debc3e6099","tid":400744,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吞完接收幾百萬飢民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對於中共來講, 其實無乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n因為中國13億人<br />\n<br />\n其實當中有超過9億, 都是活係貧窮線下<br />\n<br />\n甘肅 貴州, 四川 呢D內陸省份, 好多人既生活仲慘過北韓人"},{"pid":"2e98dd9de19c02ae44c227b626322ca64a477199","tid":400744,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"一定唔會 中國對錢有興趣<br />\n戰略部署定國土一d都唔care"},{"pid":"3d82cfd34f4135d4ae94c728f293394fd7c5a84c","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定唔會 中國對錢有興趣<br />\n戰略部署定國土一d都唔care</blockquote><br />\n唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf57581b83d032b684c779373730d007efddd90","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吞完接收幾百萬飢民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對於中共來講, 其實無乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n因為中國13億人<br />\n<br />\n其實當中有超過9億, 都是活係貧窮線下<br />\n<br />\n甘肅 貴州, 四川 呢D內陸省份, 好多人既生活仲慘過北韓人</blockquote><br />\n又唔係叫佢地過晒支國，只係易主啫，問題不大"},{"pid":"32a6a7c42037f34d73e96c99438e0902fb23263b","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cba034a2fd0bf489a6c5b41461fe39730d0e672","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e6c8abe72b5b95794423150485ff0d0524c5b48","tid":400744,"uid":73454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"一個冇軍事衛星定位既導彈系統係冇可能做到精確長程打擊，所以金仔d穿雲箭對美國影響不大，因為勁極都係一枝V2，但d左鄰右里當然會受威脅，搞到今時今日咁最大責任當然係中國管制能力唔夠，美國對待附屬國一向殘忍，一唔聽話就拉你落台，一係軍事入侵解放你，但中國已經冇能力控制北韓，佢緊係想美帝搞掂隻癲狗，但美國會等你正正式式同金仔反枱先會收拾北韓，廢事比大陸冷手執個熱煎堆"},{"pid":"7b1e20ab090a0b61cd98c004789b410f40e2b4cd","tid":400744,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"支那吞到北泡就可以直入日本海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7325678f687db826a10e853c14f633009ba8f65","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個冇軍事衛星定位既導彈系統係冇可能做到精確長程打擊，所以金仔d穿雲箭對美國影響不大，因為勁極都係一枝V2，但d左鄰右里當然會受威脅，搞到今時今日咁最大責任當然係中國管制能力唔夠，美國對待附屬國一向殘忍，一唔聽話就拉你落台，一係軍事入侵解放你，但中國已經冇能力控制北韓，佢緊係想美帝搞掂隻癲狗，但美國會等你正正式式同金仔反枱先會收拾北韓，廢事比大陸冷手執個熱煎堆</blockquote><br />\n支國個心計唔會差得過老美，控制北泡，幫美國除咗隻癲狗唔一定係好事"},{"pid":"51fd8f39faad01da3463a0b42a9509fcc5cbbc5b","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dec3390f9c3a898fc3765e9b5792766137eb44fb","tid":400744,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:04:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人識北泡文？"},{"pid":"cbc03d0c88ed15f29a9fcb322838c06526ecc161","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人識北泡文？</blockquote><br />\n同南泡唔同架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔了解"},{"pid":"2ac5dd1ffdf3d23c5bc2ce4ef31deef30ad3ae22","tid":400744,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T23:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人識北泡文？</blockquote><br />\n同南泡唔同架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔了解</blockquote><br />\n寵寵寵同撕咪打點一樣"},{"pid":"4cc6e26e2a383b4496acfe67bd716361d4ec2e87","tid":400744,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T23:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果支共真係要咁做 打完好大機會之後扶植一個政權 維持南北泡現狀</blockquote><br />\n同韓戰時候一樣有春用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40190d97805f24ac96c959858bc0a0a5d902ee9e","tid":400744,"uid":29696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T00:00:00.000Z","msg":"唔會全面吞併，就算美國南韓真係唔理你，你估戰鬥民族都會唔理？<br />\n<br />\n聽軍事方面既時事評論員講，之前美國預演打北泡，都會預留中俄邊境既地方唔侵佔，估係為左同中俄分帳<br />\n當然依家唔知侵侵會唔會咁"},{"pid":"102c158a269f5593accdf50c28d7d3cfea300c6c","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37fa1f32e16c04a4303656f812ca1c4292c427d2","tid":400744,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:55:13.000Z","msg":"點解我覺得金仔偷襲東北<br />\n東北會直接投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa1e1f22a0042edc91d680c28c811cc003adac0","tid":400744,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解我覺得金仔偷襲東北<br />\n東北會直接投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果美國, 日本偷襲東北, 東北就會直接投降<br />\n<br />\n但北韓偷襲任何一個國家, 都會有好多人奮勇抵抗<br />\n因為無人想比北韓統治"},{"pid":"579ade1dd3d827c03fd6c0fb0ae27d78d19de070","tid":400744,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼見現時金仔痴q咗線係咁對世界挑釁，老美都冇晒辦法，個個都只能依靠支國制衡北泡，如果有一日全球接納支國全面接管北泡，協助一齊打倒金仔，大家認為會有什麼影響？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問一問邊個俾飯班北泡人食，已經鳩都縮理啦"},{"pid":"cf88fcb36cd14794c1a0939a1498950a59425499","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人識北泡文？</blockquote><br />\n同南泡唔同架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔了解</blockquote><br />\n寵寵寵同撕咪打點一樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a600d09d676566c080e3d6814975756a28c52574","tid":400744,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"655f06228b78babb97abf377730e9574c9558e68","tid":400744,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"理想結局:北京、南北泡電腦大爆炸，地球上最無恥嘅兩個民族絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eafb869709b91b41de6332f1bc9c60aa4f75764","tid":400744,"uid":20284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人識北泡文？</blockquote><br />\n同南泡唔同架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔了解</blockquote><br />\n寵寵寵同撕咪打點一樣</blockquote><br />\n有分別,但北泡同南泡人大致都可以溝通到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hklinguists.wordpress.com/2010/07/28/南北韓語言上的差異/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?